{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "阿戈爾失格", "storyInfo": "在軍團的掩護下，深海獵人深入巢穴執行最後的信標投放任務。博士與烏爾比安兵分兩路，烏爾比安繼續查明真相，博士找到克萊門莎執政官質問阿戈爾對深海獵人的安排。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g12_seabed", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_underwtr", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "u"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，真難聞。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年了，他們還是懶得改良偽裝霜劑——明明可以讓它對我們和對海嗣呈現出兩種不同氣味的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別做多餘的動作，鯊魚，那樣只會讓氣味變得更重。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你一直散發出這麼濃重的海嗣氣味，我會忍不住想要砍你。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整片台地都在震動……那些蠕蟲狀的巨型海嗣正在從我們身下的岩層鑽過。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意隱蔽。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swimdeepsea", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,50", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,50", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_seabornactivity_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 1.0, "times": 10.0, "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（輕微地顫動液泡）", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_seabornactivity_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 30.0, "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（劇烈地抖動內核）", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swimdeepsea", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,50", "posto": "0,150", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,50", "posto": "0,150", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個數量，該說是海流裹挾著海嗣，還是海嗣組成了海流？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們在向前線湧去，很難想像……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很難想像前線的戰士們在遭遇什麼樣的戰鬥。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂，冷靜，不要把你的劍柄捏斷了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完成任務是對前線戰士最好的哀悼。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍團艦隊實現了對海嗣集群的牽制，我們才得以潛入巢穴深處投放信標。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕只是一株被海嗣同化的植物，也隨時可能讓我們暴露在海嗣的視線當中。前面這段路容不得一點疏忽。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，以那些枯死的巨型珊瑚為掩體，向裂谷深處下潛。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "幽靈鯊&斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1388_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swimdeepsea", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g1_beaconsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪，對吧？你上手很快。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前來我們這做職業體驗的學生，不花上一天時間理清操作流程，都很容易誤觸。你倒是在旁邊看一下子就會了。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有基礎？", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有一點點。我曾經在伊比利亞的大燈塔上工作過，燈塔和信標塔的原理稍有些相通的地方。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你的興趣是工程學，那就不奇怪了。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我做得最久的工作其實是護工。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#11$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“護工”？那是一種什麼職業？", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，就是看護老人和病人，照料他們的起居，也打理打理雜務。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，聽起來像是小幫手同時加裝153號和274號套件。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我記得小幫手是沒有人格的……對、對吧？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對的。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來很緊張，喬迪。我又不是你的阿戈爾小常識考官。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是想問，如果小幫手沒有人格，那它要怎麼應對老人或病人的情感需求？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，護工要面對的是人最脆弱、最難堪的一面。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們倒是很少因為身體上的脆弱而產生額外的情感需求。安然走向死亡的人，哪怕疾病纏身，也沒什麼難堪的。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人或病人確實可以在接受安樂死之前申請臨終對談，通常會由極富名望的哲學家或其他領域的學者來接待他們。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我完全不懂什麼哲學……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只會聊些最普通的話題，飯菜、花草與陽光之類的。但不知道為什麼，聽到的人都會很開心。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很了不起，喬迪。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明你能敏銳地把握住他人的情緒。搞不好，你在發展規劃所或者公共養育所都能找到大展身手的機會。", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我能嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#8$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不管怎麼說，還是謝謝您！這裡的儲存設備我已經重置完成了！", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很完美的操作。所以說——", "name": "信標塔技術員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等。剛剛全息影像上是不是閃過去什麼東西？", "name": "信標塔技術員"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼——", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop